----

This is a point release.

https://www.kicksecure.com/wiki/Point_Release

----

# Major Changes

* https://www.kicksecure.com/wiki/Ram-wipe has been developed. (But not yet installed by default because there is no ISO yet.)
* zsh configuration enhancements (Thanks to @nyxnor.)
* updates LKRG in the repository

----

# Upgrade

Alternatively, in-place release upgrade is possible upgrade using [Kicksecure repository](https://www.kicksecure.com/wiki/Project-APT-Repository).

